Title: [ANN][ICO] GetDoIt - GET Token
Body: I like this project. I like that the GetDoIt platform functions as an intermediary between the Client, who needs certain services and the contractor that provides them.

Author: GetDoIt_Service
Title: [ANN][ICO] GetDoIt - GET Token
Body: I would like to correct you a little bit. It is not the next country, but Germany will be the first one. Why? Because we live in Germany. We have based our company in Australia, because one if the best financial regulators that deal with blockchain and cryptocurrency is located in this state. We will expand to Australia later. However, this market is also very attractive to us. At the moment, the most important thing for us is to collect the needed amount of investments and develop the project. In 23 days we are starting crowdsale. I hope, many people will be eager to buy our tokens. But even if not, we will still develop the project as we are a venture project too. We have a business plan, tokenomics, and MVP.

Author: TimeTeller
Title: [ANN][ICO] GetDoIt - GET Token
Body: Ah okay, my bad. Thanks for that correction. I thought, the reason why it was registered first in Australia is that your platform will take off in Australia also. I'm thinking of Singapore or Estonia, where most of the ICO projects are using as the virtual place of registration. But, most of them are not really serious ones. Just want to get away from strict crypto regulations.
